  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816280/extras/aa81f93d8363dd3e642f2e0800f1f15f.poster.avif?t=1737409826\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816280/extras/aa81f93d8363dd3e642f2e0800f1f15f.webm?t=1737409826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816280/extras/aa81f93d8363dd3e642f2e0800f1f15f.mp4?t=1737409826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Immerse yourself in the battle like never before. Take over <i>any</i> tower, and become the force that turns the tide<br></li><li>From gatlings to guided missiles, the players has plenty of firepower to annihilate their enemies</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816280/extras/b81451d536bdda358eca9c14ab588fe7.poster.avif?t=1737409826\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816280/extras/b81451d536bdda358eca9c14ab588fe7.webm?t=1737409826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816280/extras/b81451d536bdda358eca9c14ab588fe7.mp4?t=1737409826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each variety of enemy requires different tactics to conquer<br></li><li>Fight off the forces of evil, and send those baddies flying<br></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816280/extras/88ccad7caf76a33d6a23896e21399a56.poster.avif?t=1737409826\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816280/extras/88ccad7caf76a33d6a23896e21399a56.webm?t=1737409826\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2816280/extras/88ccad7caf76a33d6a23896e21399a56.mp4?t=1737409826\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Freely place and upgrade towers in this complex and deep tower defense<br></li><li>Each tower has a fully fleshed out upgrade tree, allowing for a formidable defense</li></ul>",
